<br>
   <div align="left" class="article_text">
<script language="javascript" src="http://www.thesafehouse.org/news/pagebreak.js"></script>
 <script language="javascript"><!--
 var showPageNavTop = 0;
 var showPageNavBot = 1;
 var showPageNavAll = 0;
 var PageMarker = '<!--page--\>';
 var PageContent= '<div class=postbody align=left>\n<ul>\n<ul><span style="FONT-STYLE:italic">\n<div class=postbody>Update Notes: January 14, 2005 1/14/2005 7:00 AM <br><br><span style="FONT-WEIGHT:bold">*** Gameplay *** </span><br><br>\n<ul>\n<li>Changed the level of some boss encounters to better match the zone they inhabit. Rewards should also be more appropriate for the level of the encounter. <br>\n<li>Certain difficult encounters (such as those made famous by Professor Cogglesworth) will now drop a wider variety of loot. </li></ul><br><br><br><span style="FONT-WEIGHT:bold">*** Spells &amp; Combat Arts ***</span> <br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Conjurer </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L39 Vexation: Will now replenish power and health over time. <br>\n<li>L40 Geotic Brand: This spell will now increase armor class instead of decreasing it. <br>\n<li>L30 Tremor: Will now show up in the maintained window. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Necromancer</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L22 Blight: Spell will show in the maintained window. <br>\n<li>L30 Breath of the Unearthed: Will now only affect members of the target encounter, and deals disease damage and heals the Necromancer over time. <br>\n<li>L31 Withering Affliction: Will now show in the maintained window. <br>\n<li>L38 Rotting Thrall: Fixed description; it summons a zombie to do the Necromancer\'s bidding <br>\n<li>L44 Accursed Cloud: Will now only affect members of the target encounter, and deals disease damage and heals the Necromancer over time. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Bruiser</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L37 Rousing Cry: Will now affect other party members who are within range of the Bruiser. <br>\n<li>L20(Training) Velan\'s Nervy Order: Will now affect other party members who are within range of the Bruiser. <br>\n<li>L40 Heavy Scarring: Fixed description; it stuns the Bruiser while greatly increasing Crushing, Slashing, and Piercing mitigations. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Berserker </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L26 Stifled Rage: Apprentice IV versions of Stifled Rage should now work properly. <br>\n<li>L24 Battle Chant: Apprentice IV versions of Battle Chant should now work properly. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Brawler </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L10(Training) Velan\'s Taunting Cry: Now shares same reuse timer as all other group taunts (Shout, Jeer, Hand Clap, etc.). </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Paladin </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L36 Smite Prayer: Corrected the skill required from 115 to 180. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Brigand </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L36 Sap: Can now be used regardless of the Brigand\'s position relative to the target. <br>\n<li>L27 Rough Skin: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. <br>\n<li>L40 Deceit: Now grants the Brigand a 30% chance to interrupt the target on successful attacks. <br>\n<li>L41 Aegis: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Rogue</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L13 Street Smarts: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50.</li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Predator</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L13 Hunter\'s Instinct: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Assassin </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L27 Bleeder\'s Talent: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. <br>\n<li>L41 Merciless Villainy: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Ranger </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L27 Forester\'s Insight: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. <br>\n<li>L41 Veil of the Forest: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50.</li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Swashbuckler </span><br>\n<ul>\n<li>L27 Flight of Fancy: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. <br>\n<li>L41 Bladeweaver: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Dirge</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L27 Death\'s Scent: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. <br>\n<li>L41 Lithe Disbelief: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Troubador</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L41 Daelis\' Dance of Blades: Increased growth from 30 skill to 50. </li></ul><br><br><span style="TEXT-DECORATION:underline">Fury</span> <br>\n<ul>\n<li>L47 Irritating Swarm: This spell will now land on the target and other surrounding encounter members.</li></ul><br><br>- The EverQuest II Team </div></span></ul></ul></div>';
 PrintArticle();
 // -->
